                <head>No. 122.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Hoffman</persName> to Mr. <persName type="to">Fish</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">London</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1876-05-03">
                            <hi rend="italic">May</hi> 3,
                                1876</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Winslow applied for discharge. Attorney-general opposed. Case adjourned
                            ten days.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>HOFFMAN.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
